item.title: CVE-2021-25116|2024-08-03T19:56:10.649Z -- unknown -- enqueue%20anything
item.description: The Enqueue Anything WordPress plugin through 1.0.1 does not have authorisation and CSRF checks in the remove_asset AJAX action, and does not ensure that the item to be deleted is actually an asset. As a result, low privilege users such as subscriber could delete arbitrary assets, as well as put arbitrary posts in the trash.
